{"tid":1727030,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(文宣新方向) 係微博撐警 表揚香港警察 再踩低解放軍 !!!","createTime":"2019-11-16T10:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T15:31:41.000Z","uid":222970,"like":209,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"bfdfb94d36671879a7184c8cf9ce7700ee43e3cc","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:07:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">之前post過  不過今日正式出動左解放軍<br />\n先發覺我走到好前 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">係微博撐警 表掦香港警察 再踩低公安解放軍 !!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689332</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n建議文宣方向<br />\n<br />\n首先你係一個撐警藍絲<br />\n<br />\n支持警察取代解放軍！<br />\n<br />\n你要不斷煲大警察既人工 去貶低解放軍人工<br />\n<br />\n警察月薪 計埋OT 5萬以上 老解得4000一個月<br />\n<br />\n然後係微博撐警 不斷讚警察效率狂踩解放軍<br />\n<br />\n學歷 紀律 專業操守 EQ IQ 任何方面<br />\n<br />\n狂讚警察 狂踩公安解放軍 踩到佢地一文不值<br />\n<br />\n再係抖音整片拎警察同解放軍作對比<br />\n<br />\n佢封一個微博ac 再開10個<br />\n<br />\n不斷分化佢地 每日都要分化!!!!!!!! <br />\n<br />\n每一秒都要分化佢地！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察同解放軍<br />\n人工對比<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lo34Ow0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLo34Ow0.png&h=ef56a857&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGZojDG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGZojDG.png&h=5e446f7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a6ac705ff635011308e2b188b87d87c1883798a","tid":1727030,"uid":258696,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"Agree<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n_____________________<br />\n我地要做既係美國戰線阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快上twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地藍屍撐由佢地，佢係係咪都奶共架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大件事 唔好玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國會美中經濟與安全審議委員會發表年度報告，表示若果中國對香港出動解放軍或武警干預香港局勢，美國國會應該撤銷《美國-香港政策法》給予香港獨立關稅區的特殊地位。"},{"pid":"47bdc20c470999471864c87009ad0a7a029d4aea","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>建議公安部門引入香港警察出任主管職位 以提升公安工作能力</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7xMh8LM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7xMh8LM.png&h=b30ed9db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a19b0a927b9566f221480c44762014ce0d71515","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cuNhpjc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcuNhpjc.png&h=2d61e3ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fae38e1ee84de469d1e1507e33c8c02a483a0580","tid":1727030,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"［區選］藍絲散水運動，正式開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726325</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d4d010958affe76a5c7751ed22d7d1481483be9d","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>千祈唔好自稱香港警察 然後係微博話 岩岩係酒吧想同大陸妹扑野 但佢拒絕 然後話中國女人全部都係妓女 慰安婦 咁樣會挑起佢哋既中國人情緒 唔好</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d1a4b758e082f0386ab63c7dc110521137d5ad50","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:09:18.000Z","msg":"我爸爸是PPRB中的英雄, 他很厲害每天都要應付黑記的問題， 每條尖銳問題都被佢容易化解， 應該 再繼續升職 未來能取代 外交部耿爽 的官位，PPRB 每位 世叔伯都受過英國式 訓練， 不同於 耿爽 只懂得買學位， 其他世叔伯每次謙虛說 自己學歷不高 但要取代大陸官員綽綽有餘<br />\n<