umbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGZojDG.png&h=5e446f7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:16:19.000Z","msg":"P牌開唔到新貼   請手足幫手傳    <br />\n叫理大弓箭手唔好係天橋   因為可能成追擊手目標<br />\n快   幫手傳出去"},{"pid":"693d98638d890f2ad0c275aa7238ef04a8f95c8c","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d59b95740b56c106062184632c8d31db2baa39c","tid":1727030,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:17:19.000Z","msg":"緊急呼籲警察立即包圍軍營，休班警立即去九龍塘軍營外示威！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726743</a>"},{"pid":"1863b63e447c56f29dc0f4632873f4e554d52cca","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41c5b9ed8f9cfe174ce020f7724aba6099872a0","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd98f580bffa72a68e984980f54694a3fa6f8c3","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76353d358564bd90c18e3902795629456f6ef9f9","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188b0ad7a53f7a1b37d1305ce5f5ce6bdd9cb5f4","tid":1727030,"uid":15984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"香港警察在場監管解放軍執石"},{"pid":"fb54846c43d505f2672cebd922a1c3b05ec339d8","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT