islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:16:32.000Z","msg":"係咪on9嫁，班解放軍有份殺我地手足嫁"},{"pid":"afa23ad89e9f4f8f499af9d6fd887e64f718b2cb","tid":1727030,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:30:16.000Z","msg":"唔會 拉"},{"pid":"f0b8f2f8cc4486f0cbce415d4f90402cd9e8e987","tid":1727030,"uid":42299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:30:38.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"587ac5a5d0cd2d880a35a9a63ec3b6ba2479cc87","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf42ad0d85736df03052d5159835bc60d108597","tid":1727030,"uid":18476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"你係五毛定點，微博宣傳撐警？<br />\n果邊班小粉紅，你宣傳到？<br />\n不如上國際線講解放軍今日自發清潔、明日就出動坦克車打壓港人。"},{"pid":"8095a41916be2132626b64063cd3f7e1a0db8e15","tid":1727030,"uid":105668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249fb46078f0a9a4a41b819053f9ddd98b7990d2","tid":1727030,"uid":132217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bfdfb94d36671879a7184c8cf9ce7700ee43e3cc","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:07:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">之前post過  不過今日正式出動左解放軍<br />\n先發覺我走到好前 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">係微博撐警 表掦香港警察 再踩低公安解放軍 !!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689332</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n建議文宣方向<br />\n<br />\n首先你係一個撐警藍絲<br />\n<br />\n支持警察取代解放軍！<br />\n<br />\n你要不斷煲大警察既人工 去貶低解放軍人工<br />\n<br />\n警察月薪 計埋OT 5萬以上 老解得4000一個月<br />\n<br />\n然後係微博撐警 不斷讚警察效率狂踩解放軍<br />\n<br />\n學歷 紀律 專業操守 EQ IQ 任何方面<br />\n<br />\n狂讚警察 狂踩公安解放軍 踩到佢地一文不值<br />\n<br />\n再係抖音整片拎警察同解放軍作對比<br />\n<br />\n佢封一個微博ac 再開10個<br />\n<br />\n不斷分化佢地 每日都要分化!!!!!!!! <br />\n<br />\n每一秒都要分化佢地！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察同解放軍<br />\n人工對比<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lo34Ow0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLo34Ow0.png&h=ef56a857&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGZojDG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGZojDG.png&h=5e446f7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1E8THHb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1E8THHb.png&h=1ef3946d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKeep 住分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec507533bbbd7c8355a04110ec16bf9beb23369","tid":1727030,"uid":205733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1a4b758e082f0386ab63c7dc110521137d5ad50","tid":1727030,"uid":222970,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:09:18.000Z","msg":"我爸爸是PPRB中的英雄, 他很厲害每天都要應付黑記的問題， 每條尖銳問題都被佢容易化解， 應該 再繼續升職 未來能取代 外交部耿爽 的官位，PPRB 每位 世叔伯都受過英國式 訓練， 不同於 耿爽 只懂得買學位， 其他世叔伯每次謙虛說 自己學歷不高 但要取代大陸官員綽綽有餘<br />\n<br />\n強調自己受英式 訓練， 用啲大陸出名官員 提高自己地位， 咁樣得唔得呢<br />\n<br />\n轉自：隔離post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:11:06.000Z","msg":"兩邊都做<br />\n一邊支持老解<br />\n一邊支持黑警<br />\n兩邊互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2dfd20524f70c3d14e7f17b666bd9e9b2a143bb","tid":1727030,"uid":119610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}